# LITE shaders version 4.9

Original creator: Javier Garduño
Links:
https://www.planetminecraft.com/mod/makeup-ultra-fast-shader
https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/customization/makeup-ultra-fast-shader
https://github.com/javiergcim/MakeUpUltraFast

Modfied and translated by @EntokitoDezonze

Changelog:

# OVERVIEW:
- This version makes minor adjustments to the shader.

# General changes:
- Vanilla water has now smoother texture.
- Bit reduced samples on Blocky clouds, improving performance (no visual impact.)
- Slighyly adjusted clouds colors on rain.

# Bugfixes:
- Fixed ghosting on Smart TAA.
- Fixed excessive fog on Distant Horizons + Snowy biome with "Biome fog" enabled.
- Fixed some typos on potuguese language.

Version code: LT49

Based in MakeUp Ultrafast 9.3h

Olá de Entokito :) 